y water heater into a sleek spacesaving tankless design that’s packed with cutting edge technology energy conservation and long term savings for you are what drive us and our vision to use forward thinking technology to provide endless hot water for your entire home resulted in a product we’re very proud to offer it’s a sophisticated solution that means something simple to you – endless hot water visit the trutankless website our strategy   at bollente we are highly selective when identifying teams markets and business models we pursue opportunities that can achieve rapid growth and strong profitability to generate lasting returns for our shareholders disruptive innovation we are passionate about forward thinking technologies that make everyday life better for people and the environment rapid growth we look for passionate people with great ideas that have the potential to achieve rapid growth and profit active management we focus on companies that can leverage our experience and benefit from synergies with our operating subsidiaries leadership leadership the team at bollente companies hails from a diverse background collectively the team has vast knowledge and experience in building public and private companies in the cleantech webenhanced services and premium consumer products sectors robertson james orr president and ceo bollente companies inc robertson james orr has served as president  ceo of bollente companies since may  an energetic serial entrepreneur mr orr brings a wealth of strategic business development knowledge and expertise to bollente companies in  mr orr became a founding partner of bluemedia inc one of the nation’s leading signage and largeformat graphics companies headquartered in tempe arizona as the company’s sr vice president of sales and business development mr orr has led bluemedia’s impressive  annual growth rate and fostered the recent acquisition of skyline signs in  mr orr and his partners funded another venture blind society an awardwinning advertising and branding agency in scottsdale arizona blind society boasts an impressive client roster which includes the arizona cardinals att phoenix coyotes four peaks brewery warner brothers pixar entertainment and mojo yogurt mr orr graduated from arizona state university with a bachelor of arts degree in business management in  a cincinnati ohio native mr orr is socially conscious and has supported nonprofit organizations including boys  girls club of phoenix st joseph the worker muscular dystrophy association mda americans with disabilities act ada and served on the board of directors for the tempe chamber of commerce jeffrey s mayhall executive vice president as executive vice president of bollente companies inc jeffrey mayhall is actively involved in the execution of bollente investments financing recapitalizations acquisitions sales and corporate compliance most recently mr mayhall founded and led innovation credit corporation an organization dedicated to financing developing and marketing new innovative technologies and products from  –  mr mayhall served as the company’s president and grew innovation credit corporation to become one of the largest international companies within its industry prior to founding innovation credit corporation mr mayhall served as director of operations and general counsel for a large commercial real estate development company mr mayhall holds a bachelor’s degree in psychology from the university of toledo and a juris doctorate from the university of toledo college of law after graduating from law school mr mayhall relocated to arizona where he was admitted to the arizona bar and became licensed in the united state district court district of arizona investor relations news releases and supplemental company information company news stock information annual shareholder meeting information regarding bollente companies’ general annual meeting will be sent to shareholders of record sec filings request printed versions of the mos